the answer is really quite simple.<br>
Charisma and mana are equally important to a chanter.<br>
<br>
that being said int is situational in how much it helps you. as you start + mana items are much more important, since you get more from a +35 mana earring than a +5 int earring. In later levels int= more mana per there for int becomes more important than + mana items. <br>
<br>
Cha helps, any ench who doubts this fact needs to /log on, while playing and calcluate. IT HELPS.<br>
<br>
I would balance as much as possible. its not hard to get int or cha. it IS hard to get both. if i was forced to choose though i would take more mana over more Cha, since Mana= king.<br>
<br>
